Gatehouse Bank Acquires Rolls-Royce Facility for $88 Million

-- B y   D a n a   E l   B a l t a j i
-- 
2011-05-02T10:32:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-02/gatehouse-bank-acquires-rolls-royce-facility-for-88-million.html
Gatehouse Bank Plc, a Shariah-
compliant wholesale bank based in  London , acquired a Rolls-Royce
Group Plc manufacturing and logistics facility in Glasgow,
Scotland, for 52.7 million pounds ($88 million), according to a
statement e-mailed today.  The investment will yield 8 percent annually with a rental
increase of about 1.5 percent every year, the bank said. Rolls-
Royce will be the tenant until March 2028, according to the
statement, dated May 1.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dana El Baltaji in Dubai at 
 delbaltaji@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Maedler at 
 cmaedler@bloomberg.net  